.TH HIDLOOM-KEYMAP 5 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "File Formats"
.SH NAME
hidloom-keymap \- CQA02303v5 keymap JSON format
.SH DESCRIPTION
The keymap JSON defines layers, matrix positions, and resolved action names
used by logicd and the Web UI. Runtime mutable keymaps normally live under
\fB/mnt/p3/keymap.json\fR. Package defaults live under
\fB/usr/lib/hidloom/config/default/keymap.json\fR.
.SH IMPORTANT RULES
.IP \(bu 2
Treat \fB/mnt/p3\fR as device-local mutable state.
.IP \(bu 2
Do not edit package defaults as runtime state.
.IP \(bu 2
Layer, local command, text, mouse, consumer, and keyboard actions have different
output routing rules.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR logicd (8),
.BR hidloom-ctrl (1)
.br
Detailed keycode documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/keycode
